pirical abundance diagnostics. Our future work is planned to investigate\nmetal-poor HII regions with measurable T_e, in an attempt to recalibrate the\nstrong-line indices and consequently disclose the cause of the discrepancies\nbetween the empirical oxygen abundances.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Jan 2018 06:36:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 31 Jan 2018 08:02:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-14"}
