 the zero-temperature superfluid ground state\nof the system using a mean-field approach.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Jan 2018 09:25:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Jan 2018 02:56:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 1 Feb 2018 07:01:53 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 18 Mar 2018 06:23:39 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sat, 25 May 2019 14:07:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-28"}
